.TH REVIEW_WALLET_IDENTITY 1 "2026-03-29" "stophammer" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
review_wallet_identity \- inspect pending wallet identity reviews and store overrides
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B review_wallet_identity
[
.BI --db " PATH"
] [
.BI --limit " N"
] [
.B --high-confidence-only
] [
.BI --show-review " ID"
] [
.BI --show-wallet " ID"
] [
.BI --resolve-merge " ID"
.BI --target-wallet " WALLET_ID"
] [
.BI --resolve-reject " ID"
] [
.BI --resolve-class " ID"
.BI --class " CLASS"
] [
.BI --resolve-link " ID"
.BI --artist " ARTIST_ID"
] [
.BI --resolve-block-link " ID"
.BI --artist " ARTIST_ID"
] [
.B --json
]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B review_wallet_identity
lists pending wallet identity review items and allows an operator to
inspect wallet detail or store durable overrides. Pending review rows expose
review
.BR confidence ,
.BR explanation ,
and scored
.B supporting_sources
separately from the wallet's own
.BR class_confidence .
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI --db " PATH"
Path to the SQLite database. Defaults to
.BR ./stophammer.db .
.TP
.BI --limit " N"
Maximum number of review items to list. Defaults to 50.
.TP
.B --high-confidence-only
When listing pending review items, filter output to rows whose derived review
.B confidence
is
.BR high_confidence .
.TP
.BI --show-review " ID"
Show review detail plus the associated wallet detail.
.TP
.BI --show-wallet " ID"
Show wallet detail by wallet ID. Follows redirect chains.
.TP
.BI --resolve-merge " ID"
Store a merge override for the selected review item. Requires
.BR --target-wallet .
.TP
.BI --target-wallet " WALLET_ID"
Target wallet to use with
.BR --resolve-merge .
.TP
.BI --resolve-reject " ID"
Store a do-not-merge override for the selected review item.
.TP
.BI --resolve-class " ID"
Store a forced wallet classification override. Requires
.BR --class .
.TP
.BI --class " CLASS"
Classification value to use with
.BR --resolve-class .
.TP
.BI --resolve-link " ID"
Store a forced artist-link override. Requires
.BR --artist .
.TP
.BI --resolve-block-link " ID"
Store a block-artist-link override. Requires
.BR --artist .
.TP
.BI --artist " ARTIST_ID"
Artist ID to use with
.B --resolve-link
or
.BR --resolve-block-link .
.TP
.B --json
Emit machine-readable JSON instead of text output.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
List pending wallet reviews:
.nf
cargo run --bin review_wallet_identity -- --db ./stophammer.db
.fi
.TP
List only high-confidence pending wallet reviews:
.nf
cargo run --bin review_wallet_identity -- --db ./stophammer.db \\
  --high-confidence-only --limit 50
.fi
.TP
Inspect one review and its wallet:
.nf
cargo run --bin review_wallet_identity -- --db ./stophammer.db --show-review 42
.fi
.TP
Inspect a wallet directly:
.nf
cargo run --bin review_wallet_identity -- --db ./stophammer.db --show-wallet wallet-id-here
.fi
.TP
Store a merge override:
.nf
cargo run --bin review_wallet_identity -- --db ./stophammer.db \\
  --resolve-merge 42 --target-wallet wallet-id-here
.fi
.TP
Store a do-not-merge override:
.nf
cargo run --bin review_wallet_identity -- --db ./stophammer.db --resolve-reject 42
.fi
.TP
Force a wallet classification:
.nf
cargo run --bin review_wallet_identity -- --db ./stophammer.db \\
  --resolve-class 42 --class personal
.fi
.TP
Inspect scored provenance on one review item:
.nf
cargo run --bin review_wallet_identity -- --db ./stophammer.db --show-review 42
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR stophammer (1),
.BR backfill_wallets (1),
.BR review_artist_identity (1)
